{% extends "layouts/main.njk" %}

{% from "govuk/components/button/macro.njk" import govukButton %},

{% block pageTitle %}
  Declaration -Registering on behalf of someone else- Register to have your say about a national infrastructure project - National Infrastructure Planning
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
  <div class="govuk-grid-row">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds-from-desktop">

      <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">Declaration</h1>
      <p class="govuk-body">By submitting this form, you are registering to have your say and telling us your registration comments. You will be given an Interested Party reference number.</p>
      <p class="govuk-body">This means you can take part in the Examination of the application and submit more information about any of the application information. The Examining Authority must consider your views when they recommend if the project should go ahead.</p>
      <p class="govuk-body">By registering to have your say, you are agreeing that we will use your details to:</p>
      <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
        <li>contact you about the project or if we need more information</li>
        <li>let you know when you can submit more information</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="govuk-body">You are also agreeing that all comments you submit, along with your name, will be published on this website. No contact details will be made public.</p>
      <p class="govuk-body">Once your comments have been published, they cannot be removed from the website. You can withdraw your registration comments from the Examination of the project and they will no longer be taken into account.</p>

      <form autocomplete="off" action="" method="post" novalidate>

        <input type="hidden" name="declaration-confirmed" value="true">

        {{ govukButton({
          text: "Accept and register",
          type: "Submit",
          attributes: { "data-cy":"button-accept-and-regoster"}
        }) }}
      </form>

    </div>
  </div>
{% endblock %}